{"tid":1708603,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"論輸出革命（本地）","createTime":"2019-11-11T15:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T10:38:05.000Z","uid":303202,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d9202dcc1edb475574f18a6f69acc58d13fe34a0","tid":1708603,"uid":303202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:35:24.000Z","msg":"與其對外輸出，不如先團結本地人。<br />\n<br />\n《大學》：「大學之道，在明明德，在新民，在止於至善。」<br />\n<br />\n今時今日仲見到涼薄心態嘅藍絲其實好不忍，佢哋會咁都係因為只顧自身利益。<br />\n<br />\n不如試下將抗爭嘅悲劇同佢哋更貼切咁連上關係，試下勾起佢地嘅民族感或同理心。無妨，我提供簡單文宣。<br />\n<br />\n對象係沉默的街坊/手足的藍絲親人。<br />\n<br />\n雖然明顯地唔會有即時效果，亦顯想法幼稚，但願可以潛而默化、聚沙成塔。<br />\n<br />\n所謂革命，係要全港市民皆兵，方始奏效。"},{"pid":"99d8f67989f3a3e84074c92d7565379d3ac735e8","tid":1708603,"uid":303202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xJfVheR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxJfVheR.jpg&h=9ff9447d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v5wJq8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv5wJq8b.jpg&h=27dc10ad&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dU21cOc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdU21cOc.jpg&h=a003d832&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c1FRz1y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc1FRz1y.jpg&h=eb5f170e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emNXvzU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemNXvzU.jpg&h=8c2cf605&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n唯一考慮係用相片對受害人／死者家屬感受嘅影響。不過亂世中身不由己，唔好意思。"},{"pid":"7ef5296b8f13d14372249c197bf8c921142ddbd0","tid":1708603,"uid":303202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:42:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">除對外輸出之外，團結本地人都好重要。</span><br />\n<br />\n《大學》：「大學之道，在明明德，在新民，在止於至善。」<br />\n<br />\n今時今日仲見到涼薄心態嘅藍絲其實好不忍，佢哋會咁都係因為只顧自身利益。<br />\n<br />\n不如試下將抗爭嘅悲劇同佢哋更貼切咁連上關係，試下勾起佢地嘅民族感或同理心。無妨，我提供簡單文宣。<br />\n<br />\n對象係沉默的街坊/手足的藍絲親人。<br />\n<br />\n雖然明顯地唔會有即時效果，亦顯想法幼稚，但願可以潛而默化、聚沙成塔。<br />\n<br />\n所謂革命，係要全港市民皆兵，方始奏效。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f59d6917e7faddef1397fd8e8f5bbc2f5b648cfe","tid":1708603,"uid":303202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T10:38:05.000Z","msg":"以上資訊有誤"}]}